Recipe To Riches Canada - Season 3, Episode 5




Savoury Snacks

Batching up their savoury snack recipes to 1,000 pieces was no easy feat for our competitors.

Cyra Belbin, Izumi Kyle and Roshini Mellaram gave it all they had in only three hours. The results of their efforts varied from under-cooked to inconsistent. What followed was a difficult judging decision to send one competitor home and the remaining two to battle it out in a market event challenge to see if the public likes their products.




Original Air Date: 26-Mar-2014
